   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Programs status is updated to <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Completed</b> when the program life cycle is completed. After the program date (including the number of days for the grace period) has passed, and all related payout schedules are <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Closed</b> the program status is set to completed via a job which can be scheduled as often as needed.</p>
